":"April 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEach one of you has a devil-companion from the jinn over him.\u201d They said, \u201cEven you, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven me, yet Allah helped me against him until he embraced Islam.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38331,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/shaytan-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":34020,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Satan lies in wait for you to enter the mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, one of you enters the mosque, and Satan mounts him just as a man mounts his animal. If Satan becomes settled, he will collar him or bridle him.\u201d Abu Huraira said, \u201cYou can witness this.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2852,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/10\/hadha-sirat-al-mustaqeem\/","url_meta":{"origin":34020,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: This is the straight path to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, drew a line in the sand with his hand and he said, \u201cThis is the straight path of Allah.\